An experimental MLIR backend for the Exo programming language.

## Dependencies

```bash
brew install llvm pkg-config google-benchmark ninja ccache

uv venv
uv sync
source .venv/bin/activate
```

## Usage

Run the compiler:

```bash
exo-mlir <source.py> [--target {exo,builtin,scf,lowered,llvm}] [-o output.mlir]
# e.g. exo-mlir benchmarks/level1/axpy.py --target llvm -o out/axpy.mlir
```

## Benchmarks

```bash
snakemake
```

## Tests

```bash
pytest tests/
lit tests/filecheck/
```
